## Welcome to the homepage of _kramdown_!

kramdown is a *free* (GPL-licensed) library for converting text in Markdown markup to HTML. Besides
supporting the basic Markdown markup, it also supports various extensions that have been made
popular by the [PHP Markdown Extra] package and [Maruku].

The [documentation page](documentation.html) explains the usage of the library and the [syntax
page](syntax.html) has detailed information about the available syntax.

[PHP Markdown Extra]: http://michelf.com/projects/php-markdown/extra/
[Maruku]: http://maruku.rubyforge.org

